": 1642, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something nine years coming I would say since I joined the national set-up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"the national set-up\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Quahs and Sims needed to finish inside the top 13 of the 23 competing quartets to seal their spot in Paris, pending ratification by World Aquatics which will be announced on June 13.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999951342, \"rank\": 4.88827751335103e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Quahs\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"Sims\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"the 23 competing quartets\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"their spot\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"ratification\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"World Aquatics\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are Singapore's first relay side to qualify for the Olympics on merit.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5909953860173459, \"rank\": 0.6920605873595749, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"merit\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, the men's relay teams were handed universality places to compete at both the Seoul 1988 and Atlanta 1996 Games.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9896767375034917, \"rank\": 0.010169046574973733, \"text\": \"Seoul 1988\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9642247060229232, \"rank\": 0.03710265226953839, \"text\": \"Atlanta 1996\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's relay teams\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"universality places\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Hangzhou Asian Games in 2023, the same foursome were disqualified in the final - Ting Wen had dived too early during the final changeover - despite setting a time of 4:00.87 and the 31-year-old was thrilled with their latest effort.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Hangzhou Asian Games\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"the same foursome\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"the final - Ting Wen\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"the final changeover\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"their latest effort\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I am relieved, and happy too.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today was something I have been working really hard towards for the last three months, and I came here on a mission to do something great with my team.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"the last three months\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"a mission\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"my team\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What went well today was that all four of us trusted one another to all be doing what we needed to do to swim fast, and that trust took away some of the fear of the outcome.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"that trust\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the fear\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I came here wanting to redeem myself after the disappointment at the Asian Games, and I hoped that I did my teammates proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disappointment\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tan added: \\\"It's been very, very tough trying to even get the relay team to be able to compete together after the emotional turmoil everyone went through during that time.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tan\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2864}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay team\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2933}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional turmoil\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To come out of that and actually get to where we are today, it's an amazing feat.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing feat\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Under immense pressure at that point of time they did four minutes.\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"immense pressure\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"four minutes\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now we definitely are in a better condition to be able to beat that time.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better condition\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a big win for us now.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big win\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four minutes in my opinion would give us a good opportunity to drop down to a 3:58 or 3:59 eventually.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Four minutes\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3312}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"a good opportunity\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if that happens we are competitive on a top-eight position as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a top-eight position\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aside from the women's relay team, Tan was happy with the performances of the rest of his squad.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"